    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>安装RVM</h2>

<p><strong> RVM:Ruby Version Manager,Ruby版本管理器，包括Ruby的版本管理和Gem库管理(gemset) </strong></p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ curl -L get.rvm.io | bash -s stable </span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>等待一段时间后就可以成功安装好 RVM。</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ source ~/.bashrc  
</span><span class='line'>$ source ~/.bash_profile </span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>测试是否安装正常</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rvm -v</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h2>2、用RVM升级Ruby</h2>

<h1>查看当前<a href="http://ruby.taobao.org">ruby</a>版本</h1>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ ruby -v  
</span><span class='line'>ruby 1.8.7</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p></p>

<h1>列出已知的ruby版本</h1>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ rvm list known</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p></p>

<h1>安装ruby 1.9.3</h1>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ rvm install 1.9.3  </span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p><img src="https://www.baidu.com/img/baidu_jgylogo3.gif" alt="image" /></p>
